<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 04 Aug 2024 14:07:35 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>贝都因青少年在攀爬基布兹围栏后被枪杀。他的父亲正在寻求正义</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-04/ty-article-magazine/.premium/bedouin-teen-was-shot-dead-after-climbing-a-kibbutzs-fence-his-fathers-seeking-justice/00000191-1d00-d534-a9f9-7d0912850000</link><description>一名 18 岁少年被南部基布兹保安队一名涉嫌盗窃的成员杀害。这位年轻人的父亲希望有能力告诉他的孩子们，以色列仍然是一个法治国家</description><pubDate>Sun, 04 Aug 2024 13:09:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-04/ty-article-magazine/.premium/bedouin-teen-was-shot-dead-after-climbing-a-kibbutzs-fence-his-fathers-seeking-justice/00000191-1d00-d534-a9f9-7d0912850000</guid></item><item><title>特拉维夫和以色列中部报告 GPS 干扰，与 4 月伊朗袭击前夕相呼应</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-04/ty-article/.premium/gps-jamming-reported-in-tel-aviv-and-central-israel-echoing-eve-of-aprils-iran-attack/00000191-1d01-d534-a9f9-7d09a4400000</link><description>自 10 月 7 日以来，GPS 中断在以色列北部已司空见惯，但在特拉维夫却很少见。以色列国防军此前承认，卫星干扰是针对 GPS 制导无人机或导弹的主动措施</description><pubDate>Sun, 04 Aug 2024 12:22:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-04/ty-article/.premium/gps-jamming-reported-in-tel-aviv-and-central-israel-echoing-eve-of-aprils-iran-attack/00000191-1d01-d534-a9f9-7d09a4400000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军起诉寻求延长拘留涉嫌虐待斯德·泰曼的五名以色列士兵</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-04/ty-article/.premium/prosecution-seeks-extended-custody-of-five-israeli-soldiers-suspected-of-sde-teiman-abuse/00000191-1caf-db97-a7df-fcffecc00000</link><description>以色列国防军法院审查了延长八名嫌疑人还押候审的请求，这些嫌疑人被指控在被俘恐怖分子拘留中心严重虐待一名加沙被拘留者。在听证会上，检方表示，针对五名嫌疑人的证据已得到显着加强</description><pubDate>Sun, 04 Aug 2024 12:02:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-04/ty-article/.premium/prosecution-seeks-extended-custody-of-five-israeli-soldiers-suspected-of-sde-teiman-abuse/00000191-1caf-db97-a7df-fcffecc00000</guid></item><item><title>以色列在巴黎奥运会上取得空前成功的秘诀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-04/ty-article/.premium/the-secret-to-israels-success-at-the-paris-olympics/00000191-1d00-da43-afdf-3f229bc00000</link><description>多年的投资让人们对以色列在 2024 年奥运会上抱有很高的期望，但这些期望在神奇的三天里被超越了，以色列获得了六枚奥运会奖牌，其中包括一枚金牌。团队是这样做的</description><pubDate>Sun, 04 Aug 2024 11:29:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-04/ty-article/.premium/the-secret-to-israels-success-at-the-paris-olympics/00000191-1d00-da43-afdf-3f229bc00000</guid></item><item><title>特拉维夫郊区发生刺伤袭击，两名以色列人死亡，两人受伤；恐怖分子被击毙</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-04/ty-article/.premium/two-israelis-killed-two-wounded-in-stabbing-attack-suspect-shot-dead/00000191-1c49-d803-afb9-bc4b95b80000</link><description>一名66岁妇女当场被宣告死亡，一名80多岁男子在医院伤重不治身亡；以色列警方称袭击者是来自约旦河西岸的巴勒斯坦人</description><pubDate>Sun, 04 Aug 2024 10:04:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-04/ty-article/.premium/two-israelis-killed-two-wounded-in-stabbing-attack-suspect-shot-dead/00000191-1c49-d803-afb9-bc4b95b80000</guid></item><item><title>绝望的加沙人向 GoFundMe 寻求帮助。它并不总是有回报</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-08-04/ty-article-magazine/.premium/desperate-gazans-turned-to-gofundme-for-help-it-didnt-always-pay-off/00000191-08ff-dc1a-a1b7-19ff56ee0000</link><description>数以万计的巴勒斯坦人利用众筹网站筹集了重要资金，以帮助他们生存或逃离加沙地带。但有些人面临着剥削、繁文缛节、限制和延误，这可能是生死攸关的问题</description><pubDate>Sun, 04 Aug 2024 08:43:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-08-04/ty-article-magazine/.premium/desperate-gazans-turned-to-gofundme-for-help-it-didnt-always-pay-off/00000191-08ff-dc1a-a1b7-19ff56ee0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队称袭击了恐怖分子活动的加沙学校；巴勒斯坦人报告至少25人死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-04/ty-article-live/idf-about-30-rockets-fired-in-barrage-on-north-combat-soldier-seriously-wounded-in-gaza/00000191-1b5b-dd06-a3f7-9b5f2cc50000</link><description>特拉维夫郊区发生刺伤袭击，两名以色列人死亡，两人受伤；袭击者被击毙 ■ 报道：黎巴嫩南部发电厂遭到袭击 ■ 法国敦促居住在伊朗的国民“暂时离开” ■ 五枚火箭弹从加沙向以色列中部发射，其中一枚击中阿什凯隆市附近地区，没有人员伤亡报告 ■ 美联社报道称，以色列国防军的袭击在加沙造成 12 人死亡，其中 4 人在帐篷营地内 ■ 来自黎巴嫩的火箭弹落在以色列北部的拜特希勒尔 (Beit Hillel)</description><pubDate>Sun, 04 Aug 2024 03:58:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-04/ty-article-live/idf-about-30-rockets-fired-in-barrage-on-north-combat-soldier-seriously-wounded-in-gaza/00000191-1b5b-dd06-a3f7-9b5f2cc50000</guid></item><item><title>以色列准备反击伊朗，内塔尼亚胡却让公众蒙在鼓里</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-04/ty-article/.premium/as-israel-prepares-for-irans-counterattack-netanyahu-leaves-the-public-in-the-dark/00000191-19ae-db97-a7df-fdfee73e0000</link><description>与四月份不同的是，德黑兰对以色列遭受的袭击保持无线电沉默。与此同时，政府已免于向公民解释会发生什么，而总理正忙于推翻以色列国防部长的运动</description><pubDate>Sun, 04 Aug 2024 03:02:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-04/ty-article/.premium/as-israel-prepares-for-irans-counterattack-netanyahu-leaves-the-public-in-the-dark/00000191-19ae-db97-a7df-fdfee73e0000</guid></item><item><title>美国官员：拜登意识到内塔尼亚胡在人质交易上向他撒谎</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-03/ty-article/.premium/u-s-official-biden-realized-netanyahu-lied-to-him-about-hostage-deal/00000191-19c0-d051-a3f7-d9cc68ce0000</link><description>拜登政府一名高级官员告诉《国土报》，内塔尼亚胡对美国“忘恩负义”，并指出总理和拜登之间的过去两次对话既艰难又紧张</description><pubDate>Sat, 03 Aug 2024 20:32:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-03/ty-article/.premium/u-s-official-biden-realized-netanyahu-lied-to-him-about-hostage-deal/00000191-19c0-d051-a3f7-d9cc68ce0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列全国各地抗议，人质家属称内塔尼亚胡选择升级而不是达成协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-03/ty-article/.premium/israeli-hostages-families-say-pm-chose-escalation-over-deal/00000191-18f8-d116-a9db-dcfda6d00000</link><description>人质亲属发誓不会放弃要求达成人质协议的示威活动，而通常每周举行的反政府抗议活动因担心伊朗或其代理人发动袭击而被取消</description><pubDate>Sat, 03 Aug 2024 16:42:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-03/ty-article/.premium/israeli-hostages-families-say-pm-chose-escalation-over-deal/00000191-18f8-d116-a9db-dcfda6d00000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第302天：人质家属称内塔尼亚胡选择升级而不是达成协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-03/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-302-mossad-shin-bet-chief-travel-to-egypt-and-return/00000191-1913-db97-a7df-fdfb8d3f0000</link><description>以色列谈判小组高级成员告诉《国土报》，以色列国防部长认为总理内塔尼亚胡对释放人质/停火协议不感兴趣 ■ 据报道，瑞典关闭了驻贝鲁特的贝鲁特大使馆，美国、英国敦促黎巴嫩国民尽快离开该国■ 以色列摩萨德和辛贝特领导人前往埃及并返回以色列继续停战谈判 ■ 战争开始 302 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Sat, 03 Aug 2024 16:35:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-03/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-302-mossad-shin-bet-chief-travel-to-egypt-and-return/00000191-1913-db97-a7df-fdfb8d3f0000</guid></item><item><title>由于地区紧张局势和价格飙升，这些航空公司削减了飞往以色列的航班</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-03/ty-article/.premium/these-are-the-airlines-cutting-flights-to-israel-as-regional-tensions-and-prices-skyrocket/00000191-1457-db7e-a99d-1edf0f6b0000</link><description>到目前为止，所有为以色列服务的美国航空公司以及几家欧洲航空公司都已暂停航班。以色列旗舰航空公司以色列航空维持正常航班，但票价却飙升</description><pubDate>Sat, 03 Aug 2024 16:26:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-03/ty-article/.premium/these-are-the-airlines-cutting-flights-to-israel-as-regional-tensions-and-prices-skyrocket/00000191-1457-db7e-a99d-1edf0f6b0000</guid></item><item><title>官员警告称，恐怖组织利用阿拉伯犯罪组织袭击以色列</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-03/ty-article/.premium/arab-crime-organizations-being-used-by-terror-groups-to-attack-israel-officials-warn/00000191-18ad-d4cf-afb5-5cfdf97d0000</link><description>以色列国防官员警告部长们，“有组织犯罪对国家安全构成战略威胁”，并警告外国恐怖组织已经试图利用以色列境内的犯罪组织实施袭击。</description><pubDate>Sat, 03 Aug 2024 15:39:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-03/ty-article/.premium/arab-crime-organizations-being-used-by-terror-groups-to-attack-israel-officials-warn/00000191-18ad-d4cf-afb5-5cfdf97d0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列人阿尔乔姆·多尔戈皮亚特在巴黎奥运会体操自由体操决赛中获得银牌</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/sports/london-2012/olympics-news/2024-08-03/ty-article/.premium/israeli-gymnast-artem-dolgopyat-clinches-silver-medal-at-paris-olympics-gymnastics-final/00000191-188d-dd1b-a9f5-ff8d36ec0000</link><description>多尔戈皮亚特的胜利使以色列的奥运奖牌总数达到 19 枚，其中 6 枚是在 2024 年巴黎奥运会上获得的</description><pubDate>Sat, 03 Aug 2024 14:27:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/sports/london-2012/olympics-news/2024-08-03/ty-article/.premium/israeli-gymnast-artem-dolgopyat-clinches-silver-medal-at-paris-olympics-gymnastics-final/00000191-188d-dd1b-a9f5-ff8d36ec0000</guid></item><item><title>10 月 7 日，以色列人质埃坦·利维 (Eitan Levy) 的家人公布了加沙人踢打、虐待他身体的视频</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-03/ty-article/.premium/family-of-israeli-hostage-eitan-levy-release-footage-of-gazans-abusing-his-body-on-oct-7/00000191-186a-d053-a7ff-5bfee3bd0000</link><description>利维于 10 月 7 日被杀，他的尸体被运往加沙。视频显示，利维的尸体在一辆汽车的敞开的后备箱中，后来躺在地上，而加沙人则对其进行拳打脚踢。 Levy是一名53岁的出租车司机，10月7日在载着一名乘客前往加沙边境时被杀</description><pubDate>Sat, 03 Aug 2024 14:10:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-03/ty-article/.premium/family-of-israeli-hostage-eitan-levy-release-footage-of-gazans-abusing-his-body-on-oct-7/00000191-186a-d053-a7ff-5bfee3bd0000</guid></item><item><title>《国土报》摄影师拍摄的以色列一周</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-03/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israels-week-in-pictures/00000191-1865-dd1b-a9f5-ff6d46a00000</link><description></description><pubDate>Sat, 03 Aug 2024 13:56:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-03/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israels-week-in-pictures/00000191-1865-dd1b-a9f5-ff6d46a00000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队袭击约旦河西岸图尔卡尔姆；巴勒斯坦人报告九人死亡，其中包括哈马斯指挥官</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-03/ty-article/israeli-army-strikes-west-bank-palestinians-report-nine-dead-including-hamas-commander/00000191-17a4-df57-afd7-f7b633bd0000</link><description>以色列国防军表示，他们使用无人机在图尔卡尔姆击落了一辆载有恐怖分子的车辆，并声称车内人员正在前往发动袭击的路上。军队第二次袭击图尔卡姆，目击者称两次袭击造成九人死亡</description><pubDate>Sat, 03 Aug 2024 13:38:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-03/ty-article/israeli-army-strikes-west-bank-palestinians-report-nine-dead-including-hamas-commander/00000191-17a4-df57-afd7-f7b633bd0000</guid></item><item><title>汤姆·鲁文尼 (Tom Reuveni) 夺得金牌，莎朗·坎特 (Sharon Kantor) 夺得银牌；以色列奖牌数增至五枚，创本届奥运会历史最高奖牌数</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-03/ty-article/.premium/israeli-sharon-kantor-wins-olympic-silver-tom-reuveni-guarantees-medal-at-semi-finals/00000191-181a-d68e-a79b-5b9fdb110000</link><description>21 岁的坎特 (Kantor) 在女子组比赛中获得银牌后不久，23 岁的鲁文尼 (Reuveni) 在 IQFoil 组别中赢得了金牌。这些奖牌使以色列的奥运奖牌总数达到 18 枚，其中 5 枚是在 2024 年巴黎奥运会上获得的</description><pubDate>Sat, 03 Aug 2024 12:10:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-03/ty-article/.premium/israeli-sharon-kantor-wins-olympic-silver-tom-reuveni-guarantees-medal-at-semi-finals/00000191-181a-d68e-a79b-5b9fdb110000</guid></item><item><title>报告：哈尼亚遇刺后希腊“高度戒备”针对以色列目标的袭击</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2024-08-03/ty-article/greece-on-high-alert-for-attack-against-israeli-targets-after-haniyeh-assassination/00000191-1754-d68e-a79b-5fd5abee0000</link><description>据希腊《Kathimerini》报纸报道，希腊当局正在与外国情报机构联系，了解有关雅典以色列或犹太人目标遭受袭击的威胁加剧的报道。</description><pubDate>Sat, 03 Aug 2024 10:18:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2024-08-03/ty-article/greece-on-high-alert-for-attack-against-israeli-targets-after-haniyeh-assassination/00000191-1754-d68e-a79b-5fd5abee0000</guid></item><item><title>报道：以色列摩萨德雇佣伊朗特工在哈马斯头目哈尼亚的房间里放置炸药</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-03/ty-article/report-israels-mossad-hired-iranian-agents-to-plant-explosives-in-hamas-chiefs-room/00000191-16fa-db7e-a99d-1efa23980000</link><description>伊朗消息人士告诉《每日电讯报》，负责高级官员安全的革命卫队特工在哈马斯领导人被杀的德黑兰宾馆的另外两个房间里安放了爆炸装置</description><pubDate>Sat, 03 Aug 2024 07:41:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-03/ty-article/report-israels-mossad-hired-iranian-agents-to-plant-explosives-in-hamas-chiefs-room/00000191-16fa-db7e-a99d-1efa23980000</guid></item></channel></rss>